# OpMech-GraphRAG: Commutator-Guided Explore/Exploit Implementation

## Project Context

You are implementing the **OpMech-GraphRAG** system on top of an existing MoE-built knowledge graph. The graph is stored in Neo4j and contains Apple SEC filings (10-K, 10-Q) from FY2022-FY2024.

### Existing Infrastructure
- **Neo4j Database**: `bolt://localhost:7687`
- **Graph Statistics**: 1,737 nodes, 26,842 edges, 1 connected component
- **LLM**: Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct via vLLM at `http://localhost:8000/v1`
- **Embeddings**: FinBERT (768 dimensions) stored in `data/embeddings/`

### Node Types
- `FINANCIAL_LINE` (963 nodes) - XBRL financial data
- `ENTITY` (516 nodes) - Extracted entities
- `NOTE` (163 nodes) - Footnotes to financial statements
- `TEXT_SECTION` (95 nodes) - MD&A, Risk Factors, Business sections

### Edge Types
- `CAUSED_BY`, `LEADS_TO` - Causal relationships
- `MENTIONS_ENTITY`, `ENTITY_RELATED_TO` - Entity relationships
- `TEMPORAL_NEXT` - Time-based links across periods
- `REFERS_TO` - Cross-references
- `DISCUSSES`, `EXPLAINS_LINE_ITEM` - Table-text connections
- `SEMANTICALLY_SIMILAR` - Semantic similarity

### Node Properties
- `id`: Unique identifier (e.g., `AAPL-10-K-FY2022_TS_0006`)
- `type`: Node type
- `text`: Content text (truncated to 2000 chars)
- `filing_id`: Source filing (e.g., `AAPL-10-K-FY2022`)
- `period`: Time period (e.g., `FY2022`, `Q1-2024`)
- `section`: Document section (e.g., `Item 1A`, `Item 7`)
- `xbrl_tag`: XBRL taxonomy tag (for FINANCIAL_LINE)
- `value`: Numeric value (for FINANCIAL_LINE)

### Edge Properties
- `id`: Unique identifier
- `type`: Edge type
- `expert`: Creating expert (e.g., `CausalChainBuilder`)
- `confidence`: Confidence score (0.0 - 1.0)
- `evidence`: Supporting evidence text

